\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 But there was nothing in Spencer Street or round there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Very little in Liverpool at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No. No, I don't remember anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You had no tutor or governess did you? How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 When you first started what time in the morning did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 And when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
Used to come home for dinner between twelve and one. And then - used to leave school at four o'clock and call at me grandma's see if she wanted any messages, that was my constant job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 So you went to school full time at the age of five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Stay Street - board school. But I remember it being turned to - council school - I well remember that - writing that on 
the - exercise book you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did I get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did your mother take you or older sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh no, no, I was the eldest girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did your elder brother take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No. Once I was taken I could find my way then there was friends round that went to the same school. Was quite a lot went to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 That was Stay street board school or council school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 So your mother took you at first then you were able to find your way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You came home for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You did describe what you had for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I loved it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You did like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 They were the finest in the world - bar none - bar none.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did the teachers emphasi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804522\charrsid6432729 z}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 e any certain things important in life, such as manners. Punctuality, tidiness, way of speaking, honesty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well honesty - and - the way to sit at the desk and how to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804522\charrsid6432729 
 speak of course. We had marvel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
ous teachers - the finest in the world bar none. And as I say, to this day - old and all as I am I well remember them all. About fifty or sixty in a class in those days but they were teachers. They definitely were teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 If you did something the teachers didn't like what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I'd get the - the - the signal on me that was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What's the signal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Clipper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What's a clicker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Have you never heard of a signal? It was - it - big head and it
 - it - it clicked like that - say you were marching. Well I remember one time I got the - I did something, I was talking I suppose - I got it on me knuckle and me hand swelled. And me gran took me along to Miss Morgan, she lived in Auberry Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Who's Miss Morgan?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
One of me teachers. She took me round to Miss Mor - of course she knew them of course all teachers round that district - took me round to Miss Morgan and I - how dared she do such - such a thing to me - 'cos here was nobody like me. 
So - she said, and here, she can't go to her music lessons. I can see Bella Morgan's face you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You were hiding behind your grandmother there all right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh I'll say. But I well remember that. Oh I do. Nobody dared touch me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did they ever hit you with anything at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
Only the signal on your knuckles. And then we had to - if we was talk - we were talking when we shouldn't be talking - we had to write five hundred times - disobedience or something like that. 'Course we'd get so far and then we'd be told to go home.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did they punish the boys the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I don't know, Alan will tell you that, he went to Stay Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did they punish them for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Play truant I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did they punish the girls for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Talking. Need you ask that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did your parents take an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh yes. My mother did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did they ask what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did they visit the school or meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well mother hadn't time to go to teachers - my gran did it all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well we always said so and so's her favourite you know. You know, they brought her flowers or anything like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Were there any gangs or groups as school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Were any children in school left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you go to another school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No, the one school. We all went to the one school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No. No I was - my mother needed help at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you attend any part time education afterwards such as evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No Oh - I went to night school. I went to Hayworth Street night school to learn dressmaking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Do you have any regrets about your education.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 None whatsoever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Do you think you benefited by attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 We'll talk about your first full time job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I think it was in the Echo adverts, you know. And I went to a - mi
llinery was my first job in Bowes Street. I got bored stiff running on silk - running - sewing on silks and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Sew - on pieces of silks - just run you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 That was as an apprentice was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I was only - I was only fourteen. And I wasn't there very long. When I - I gave that up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What were the hours there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I think it was from nine 'til six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What about Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Nine to one I think it would be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 And Sunday you didn't work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you have holidays with pay there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No. I wasn't there long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What was the rate of wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I think this was only a shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you feel it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you do with the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I gave it to me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did she spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get on with the other people at that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 But you didn't like the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No, I felt as thought I was - superior to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did it alter your attitude to school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Now about your second job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I went to the tailoring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Where at?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 In Drury Lane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I think I got it through the paper. And - it was a very good job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you have to do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
Used to make collars - and buttonholes. In the tailoring you know - it - the canvas underneath the canvas. I used to do the canvas - canvas collars and - and they were very nice 
people I worked with. There was only the - oh, there was the cutter then there was the - tailor himself and then there was the machinist. And they were very, very nice people. Very nice.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You got on very well with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Got on very well indeed. But - I got tired of that job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What were the hours there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well that was similar - nine to five - six - nine to six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 And the wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well I was serving me time you know. Wouldn't be much. I was serving me time. And - I gave that jo
b up. Mind you - my mother really needed me at home but she wanted me to have something I could turn to. You see. She wanted me to have something that I could turn to if ever I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15802361 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729  and needed any - which was a good idea. But the next job I got was a very, very good job. I was a - extraordinary good writer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
Through a - influence of me gran's. In fact it was my gran's - daughter-in-law's brother-in-law, it comes to that. He lived - he lived in Spencer Street. Fiddl
er. Yes. Well he - knew - bossed in this - the Law Integrity Insurance Company. And it was right opposite Elliot Street. Used to be - a coffee's caf\'e9
 underneath I think. And it was a nice - very nice offices - very nice - building altogether. It's not there now of course. And the hours were ten 'til four and I got five shillings a week. Well remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you work on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No. Ten to four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I don't think I was there long enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you think that was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Very good - five shillings and ten to four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you give the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh every time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did she give you any back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh yes. I never went short.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get on with the other people there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 All right - very well indeed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you think about the employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Very well - very nice - gentleman. Without a doubt. But you see -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did that job change your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No. No. Well the reason - my mother wanted
 me to stay at home because after all seven of us was a - a lot. A big job. And she badly wanted me to stay at home. But I got a bit restless and then she'd let me - yes, that' - right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How long were you at this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh I'd be - I don't think I'd be any more than twelve - and it was a wonderful job. I used to write the proposals out. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What made you leave it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Because my mother wasn't well and, you see, it was a bit too much for her really you know. But she really needed me at home very, very b}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804522\charrsid6432729 ad}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 ly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What about your next job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Now I think -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Up to the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh well I - I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15802361 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
 the beginning of the first world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 But up to being }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15802361 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 ?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well - I was at home with my mother. Yes. 'Cos she wasn't in good health then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You helped your mother did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 I helped my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you do any jobs since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Have I done any? Only during this last war - I went as part time - I was in the British American doing t
he service work - packing the cigarettes or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Were you called up for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh no, no. No, I did it - I thought it - Bob thought it'd take me mind off the boys - three of them all away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Three of your boys were away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes. I was only fre
tting. And he - she thought - he thought that'd be good for me si it was only like eight to one - I was home at one o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 That's the only other job you've done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 That's the job, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well of course they were wanting everybody and - I mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did you do - packing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Packing cigarettes for the forces. Packing and checking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you work on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh I was there a couple of years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did you get holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Do you remember the rate of pay you got?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
I don't know, but they finished up when the - when the war was over, they finished up and they gave us - so much money for the time - a kind of bonus.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 It used to be a good job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 It was, but oh by God we used to work. Oh. I said -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 That was in Commercial Road wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes. 'Course with me I've always - if ever I went to a job and I - anyone turened funny with me, oh I'd say, ta-ra. I - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You were able to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh I was in the position to do it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You can imagine what it must have been like for other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 It must have been terrible mustn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 So that's all your work is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Yes.
