 letters Flo, all written. I say, you're mad, you know. Well I - mind you, I'm getting a bit shaky now but - everyone passes remark. Even the - when I sign me - in the Post Office. You write a good hand. Well, funny thing my husband wasn't much - good wri
ter. But I mean he never used to pass me out a compliment. Of course, he said, it's understandable. Plain - well that's all you want don't it.
