\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Did it change your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No.
