 the same time. It seems that they had to postpone theirs on account of the conditions and we were both }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15802361 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 
 at the same time. And I can always remem - the - Minister saying, well seeing as we have one off the land and one off the sea, we'll play God save the King. Well my husb
