r-in-law's still alive and she's well over eighty. That's right - comes to point. Yes. And it was really old fashioned then with the big paraffin lamps you know. Oh it was beautiful place. I had my breakfast there - wedding breakfast. And I had - my husba
nd - my best man all in khaki and Edith my bridesmaid. It was very quiet really. But it was very nice. Nice to look back on.
