\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 The Corporation were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh they were, yes, they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 He came back out of the Army and went back on tram driving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 What did he do after that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well - I mean to say the - he got the union.
