\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 No, from there we went to sixty Whitechapel. And from Whitechapel they went to Edge Lane. I know they were there - yes.
