\insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 lor - yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How long was he a City Coun}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804522\charrsid6432729 se}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 lor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 You told me you worked after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15802361 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
