\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12474242 FM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 Well he thought it was g
ood for me because the - he knew I was fretting about the boys. He thought it was best for me to go. He didn't mind at all - he was very very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid927397 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5862339\charrsid6432729 How did you think your husband felt about his work - did he like it or dislike it?
